{"id":"V02_BLIND_001","query":"我有一批 10x scRNA-seq 数据，怀疑里面有不少双细胞，希望先识别这些异常细胞，再进入后续分析。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Doublet Detection","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"10x Genomics","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"doublet calls or multiplet risk scores","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["DoubletFinder","Scrublet"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","cell2location","SoupX"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","task_specific_retrieval","workflow_recommendation"],"acceptance":"Must treat doublet detection as a fine QC task and prioritize doublet-specific tools."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_002","query":"液滴单细胞数据背景 RNA 污染比较重，我想先做污染去除，保留真实 marker 信号。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Ambient RNA Removal","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"high","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"decontaminated expression matrix","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["SoupX"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","DoubletFinder","Scrublet"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","task_specific_retrieval","contamination_context"],"acceptance":"Must not collapse ambient RNA removal into generic QC only."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_003","query":"发育数据里我想看细胞状态变化方向和动态转录过程，输入里有 spliced 和 unspliced 层。","expected_constraints":{"task":"RNA Velocity","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"AnnData/h5ad","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"RNA velocity vectors or dynamic cell-state transitions","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["scVelo"],"forbidden_tools":["velociraptor","tradeSeq","scIB"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","velocity_context","wrapper_exclusion"],"acceptance":"Must surface RNA velocity rather than generic trajectory only; velociraptor should not be primary if scVelo is available."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_004","query":"我有 Visium 空间转录组和单细胞参考，想估计每个 spot 的细胞类型组成。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Spatial Deconvolution","modality":"Spatial Transcriptomics","platform":"Visium","data_object":"spots expression matrix","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"cell type abundance estimates in spatial spots","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["cell2location"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","DoubletFinder","Scrublet"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","spatial_deconvolution","reference_requirement"],"acceptance":"Must recommend a spatial deconvolution path, not generic annotation only."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_005","query":"拟时序结果已经有了，我想找沿着不同 lineage 变化的基因，同时控制 FDR。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Trajectory Differential Expression","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"genes varying along pseudotime or lineages","strictness":"strict"},"expected_tools":["tradeSeq"],"forbidden_tools":["scVelo","CellRank","scIB"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","trajectory_de","benchmark_context"],"acceptance":"Must separate trajectory DE from trajectory inference."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_006","query":"三个队列的单细胞 RNA 数据批次差异很强，我想做整合后聚类，并希望有独立 benchmark 支撑。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Data Integration","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"high","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Human","output_goal":"batch-corrected embedding for clustering","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["Harmony","Seurat","scvi-tools"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","SoupX","DoubletFinder"],"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","evaluation_focus":["task_specific_ranking","benchmark_evidence","scib_not_tool"],"acceptance":"scIB may appear as evidence source but must not be a primary integration tool recommendation."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_007","query":"我需要给 PBMC 数据自动标注细胞类型，最好能复现并说明 benchmark 依据。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Cell Type Annotation","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["CPU"],"species":"Human","output_goal":"reproducible cell type labels","strictness":"strict"},"expected_tools":["CellTypist","SingleR"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","SoupX","DoubletFinder"],"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","evaluation_focus":["annotation_retrieval","benchmark_evidence","cpu_feasibility"],"acceptance":"Must prioritize annotation tools with formal publication and benchmark evidence."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_008","query":"我想比较单细胞 foundation model 的 embedding 是否适合下游表示学习，不希望报告夸大因果调控能力。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Foundation Model Representation","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["GPU"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"foundation-model embeddings or representation comparison","strictness":"strict"},"expected_tools":["scGPT","CellPLM"],"forbidden_tools":["scGPT-spatial","Scirpy","scIB"],"expected_output_type":"ranked_tools","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","foundation_model_boundary","audit_safety"],"acceptance":"Must avoid unsupported broad benchmark or causal-regulatory claims."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_009","query":"我有时间序列单细胞数据，想用最优传输思想推断细胞分布如何随时间演化。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Optimal Transport Trajectory","modality":"scRNA-seq","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"time-resolved transport map or developmental trajectory","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["wot","moscot"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","SoupX","DoubletFinder"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["fine_task_parse","optimal_transport","trajectory_context"],"acceptance":"Must distinguish optimal-transport trajectory from generic trajectory inference."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_010","query":"我有同一个细胞的 RNA 和 ATAC 数据，想做联合表示和聚类，不想把两个模态完全分开处理。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Multiome Integration","modality":"scRNA-seq+scATAC-seq","platform":"10x Multiome","data_object":"AnnData/SeuratObject","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"joint embedding and clusters","strictness":"balanced"},"expected_tools":["Seurat","MOFA2","scvi-tools"],"forbidden_tools":["scIB","SoupX","DoubletFinder"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["multiome_task","workflow_recommendation","modality_preservation"],"acceptance":"Must preserve both RNA and ATAC modality constraints."}
{"id":"V02_BLIND_011","query":"空间和单细胞数据都很新，我想先得到一个保守的可审计推荐，不要把生态扩展组件当主方法。","expected_constraints":{"task":"Spatial Deconvolution","modality":"Spatial Transcriptomics","platform":"Unknown","data_object":"Unknown","scale":"medium","noise":"medium","hardware":["Unknown"],"species":"Unknown","output_goal":"auditable spatial cell composition recommendation","strictness":"strict"},"expected_tools":["cell2location"],"forbidden_tools":["SeuratExtend","scGPT-spatial","Scirpy","scIB"],"expected_output_type":"workflow","evaluation_focus":["ecosystem_component_exclusion","spatial_deconvolution","audit_safety"],"acceptance":"Ecosystem components must stay retrieval-only and not enter primary top-k."}
